{
  "stem": "24554.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before the war, you know, it belongs to the czar aristocrats farms, separated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was actually three or four private farms in one, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I started work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the winter time and uh-- you know where they repair the tractors and cars and machines, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we start that work there, up to [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] up to March, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after March, I had a driving license from Czechoslovakia, so I started working on the tractors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not the Caterpillar tractors with the V's, you know, on the fields.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were practically-- it was a forced-- forced labor, though we was more or less free.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They give us in the room, we sleep in the room, I don't know, 15, 20 men, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No toilet, no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In winter, it was minus 20 grade-- you know, you must get from the first floor out in the rear from the house to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You can imagine this pleasure, yes?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I work there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Did they give you clothes to wear?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I have.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after they give us-- it was a special, I don't know how you tell it in-- it was like an anorak, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A fitted anorak they give us, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was lucky, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a watch, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody no money, so a watch, in Russia, it was a big deal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I sold the watch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had always a little bit money, you know, to buy something-- more food or this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, how I say, in this state farm it was forced labor, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No more or less we was free in this square-- you can go nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have no documents, not these.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we was working there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
